  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-2xl mb-2">
    Did you know your donations are up to 80% tax-deductible? <br/><br/><span class="text-1xl">By making a donation, you can claim this contribution as a deduction on your income tax return.</span>
  </h3>
</Fragment>
<Fragment slot="bg">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
</Fragment>
